Detailed Description

Component used for triggering of the document import/export command from the file menu of a document based application.

virtual const ibase::IHierarchicalCommand* iqtdoc::CDocumentImportExportCommandComp::GetCommands ( ) const
virtual

Get list of menu commands.

These commands will be integrated in global menu system, independent from actual selected view. For support of normal pull down menu, depth of this tree structure should be at least 3.
